flowchart TD
    Start([Editor opens admin]) --> Create{Create new page?}
    Create -->|New page| CreateForm[Create Page form]
    Create -->|Edit existing| EditForm[Edit Page form]

    CreateForm --> SaveChoice1{Save button}
    SaveChoice1 -->|Save as Draft| DraftCreate[Page saved<br/>Workspace stays Open]
    SaveChoice1 -->|Create| CreateStd[Page saved<br/>Workspace stays Open]

    EditForm --> SaveChoice2{Save button}
    SaveChoice2 -->|Save as Draft| DraftEdit[Changes saved<br/>Workspace stays Open]
    SaveChoice2 -->|Save| SaveStd[Changes saved<br/>Workspace stays Open]

    DraftCreate --> Open
    CreateStd --> Open
    DraftEdit --> Open
    SaveStd --> Open

    Open([Workspace: Open]) -->|Editor: Submit for approval| InReview
    Open -->|Editor: Save as Draft<br/>loops back| Open

    InReview([Workspace: InReview]) -->|Reviewer: Approve| Approved
    InReview -->|Reviewer: Reject<br/>with notes| Open

    Approved([Workspace: Approved]) -->|Release Mgr: Publish| Publishing
    Approved -->|Release Mgr: Schedule| Scheduled

    Scheduled([Workspace: Scheduled]) -->|Cron job at publish_at| Publishing
    Scheduled -->|Release Mgr: Unschedule| Approved

    Publishing([Workspace: Publishing]) -->|Atomic flip| Published

    Published([Workspace: Published<br/>Page is live]) -->|Release Mgr: Rollback| Rollback[Previous version restored]

    classDef editor fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,color:#1e3a8a
    classDef reviewer fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f
    classDef release fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#14532d
    classDef terminal fill:#fce7f3,stroke:#db2777,color:#831843

    class DraftCreate,CreateStd,DraftEdit,SaveStd,Open editor
    class InReview reviewer
    class Approved,Scheduled,Publishing release
    class Published,Rollback terminal
